*Svrhe* je da se postigne cilj. (The purpose is to achieve the goal.)

*Svrše* li se svi zadaci, biće završen projekat. (If all tasks are completed, the project will be finished.)

Da bi se postigla *svrha*, potrebno je znati šta je cilj. (In order to achieve the purpose, it is necessary to know what is the goal.)

Svi su se složili u *svrhu* uspešnog projekta. (Everyone agreed for the purpose of successful project.)

U *svrhe* postizanja uspeha, potrebno je puno rada. (In order to achieve success, a lot of work is required.)